  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DOPED GAMES IS PROUD TO PRESENT:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"HELLGATE SENIGALLIA REMAKE\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(from the Level designer of <strong>Grezzodue2</strong>, developer of <strong>Topolino Amico delle Guardie</strong>, <strong>Hellgate Senigallia</strong>, and <strong>Deep</strong>).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the adventure and fight off hordes of paranormal beings in this old-school FPS (boomer shooter) with dark and mysterious tones! Save the small town of Senigallia (not everything can happen in New York!), stop the advancing evil, and show what you're made of! New weapons, 12 massive levels, new enemies, new quests, new NPCs, a completely revamped RPG gameplay, and an epic original soundtrack! (Sik, Steven Larsen, Rick Dope, Above The Tree, Between Balls and Ass...)!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DOPED GAMES IS PROUD TO PRESENT:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"HELLGATE SENIGALLIA REMAKE\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(from the Level designer of <strong>Grezzodue2</strong>, developer of <strong>Topolino Amico delle Guardie</strong>, <strong>Hellgate Senigallia</strong>, and <strong>Deep</strong>).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the adventure and fight off hordes of paranormal beings in this old-school FPS (boomer shooter) with dark and mysterious tones! Save the small town of Senigallia (not everything can happen in New York!), stop the advancing evil, and show what you're made of! New weapons, 12 massive levels, new enemies, new quests, new NPCs, a completely revamped RPG gameplay, and an epic original soundtrack! (Sik, Steven Larsen, Rick Dope, Above The Tree, Between Balls and Ass...)!</p>",
